## **Complete Channel Plugin Reference Guide**

I've analyzed the IRC and Nostr channel plugins in the OpenClaw repo. Here's the complete structure and patterns you need to create your "pulseboard" channel plugin:

### **Directory Structure**

```
extensions/
├── irc/                          # IRC channel plugin
│   ├── index.ts                  # Main entry point
│   ├── setup-entry.ts            # Setup wizard entry
│   ├── package.json              # Package metadata
│   ├── openclaw.plugin.json      # Plugin manifest
│   ├── api.ts                    # Public API barrel
│   ├── channel-config-api.ts     # Config API exports
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── channel.ts            # Main ChannelPlugin definition
│   │   ├── runtime.ts            # Runtime storage
│   │   ├── types.ts              # Type definitions
│   │   ├── accounts.ts           # Account resolution
│   │   ├── config-schema.ts      # Config schema definitions
│   │   ├── setup-core.ts         # Setup adapter logic
│   │   ├── setup-surface.ts      # Setup wizard UI
